data.description: Discover the perfect blend of city convenience and suburban charm in this delightful Highland Park home, nestled on a generous corner lot. Step inside to find the warmth and character of beautiful original wood floors that seamlessly blend vintage charm with modern living. Enjoy the privacy and space of a corner lot, offering plenty of room for outdoor activities and landscaping. Host barbecues, entertain guests, or simply bask in the sun on the expansive backyard deck, providing ample outdoor living space. Protect your vehicle from the elements with the convenience of covered parking right on the property. This home has everything you need for a comfortable, stylish lifestyle. New roof and exterior paint in 2023.
